narratives.question_text: How would you summarize ECON 110 05 for a fellow student? Would you recommend ECON 110 05 to another student? Why or why not?
comments: If you're going to take Engl 120, do it with Professor McCabe. She's super experienced and knowledgeable!

Good course. Sometimes, Professor McCabe's comments are really nitpicky and make no sense and it can be frustrating. But she's a really nice person, and students should take advantage of her office hours.
I highly recommend taking ENGL 120. It's a great chance to explore one's own writing style. DO NOT take it with Allyson McCabe.
